block content
  h2 Note Taking
  p Taking high quality notes is one of the most important things you can do as your go through this course. The act of recording your thoughts in your own words helps you understand the material better. Also, you will need to come back to your notes in the future to remember things you have forgotten. Watch the video below for some more advice on how to take great notes

  p
    iframe(width="1120",height="630",src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E7CwqNHn_Ns",title="YouTube video player",frameborder="0",allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen)

  p You can decide where you want to keep your notes and how to organize them in a way that is most helpful to you! Google Docs is one simple option.  You could keep all your notes in your fork of this Github repo. If you want something more complex you could look at&nbsp;
    a(href="https://obsidian.md/",target="_blank") Obsidian
    span &nbsp;. You can even use physical notebooks and notecards, for some people the act of writing helps them remember things better.

  p Regardless of which option you choose keep these notes handy because you will want to keep reviewing them again and again.

  p.hint Every video you watch you should always take time to write down some of your notes on what you learned!
